  "text": "A channel matrix treatement of an O-MIMO system using MGDM technique should be simple and pragmatic, since MMFs are used in short-range applications where simplicity and low cost are key issues. We propose here a transfer matrix decomposition method which can be divided into 3 stages: noise whitening, channel diagonalization and dimension reduction. The diagonalization of a MGDM link will be through a precoding matrix F and a decoding matrix G. When the matrix is diagonal, the equivalent noise system is white and isotropic [CITATION_1] . The system until now can be written as:",
